  "description": "Welcome to your perfect coastal retreat — a stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home set within the peaceful and exclusive gated community in the La Quinta area. This stylish property offers the ideal blend of relaxation, comfort, and access to some of the most beautiful surroundings on the Costa del Sol.\n\nInside, the home exudes a calm and contemporary feel. The main living area is spacious and filled with natural light, featuring comfortable seating, a dining area, and large glass doors that open out to a sun-drenched terrace. The kitchen is fully equipped with modern appliances and ample space for home-cooked meals. All three bedrooms are tastefully styled, with the master offering an en-suite bathroom, creating a tranquil and inviting atmosphere perfect for both short stays and longer escapes.\n\nThe outdoor area is designed for enjoyment, with a generous terrace overlooking lush gardens and the rolling hills of La Quinta. It’s the perfect spot to unwind with a morning coffee or dine al fresco as the sun sets. Just steps away, the beautifully maintained communal pool provides a refreshing escape on warm days, surrounded by greenery and views of the natural landscape.\n\nSituated in Altos de La Quinta, this home offers the serenity of a hillside setting while still being just a short drive from the buzzing lifestyle of Marbella and Puerto Banús. The area is known for its prestigious golf course, La Quinta Golf & Country Club, and is close to a variety of restaurants, wellness centres, and local markets — offering the best of both convenience and tranquility.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.",
